    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolute showroom condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot. It\u2019s been pampered since day one and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. If you're looking for total perfection and a ride that's been treated like royalty, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
